data.description:
Welcome to your next home at 1977 Gail Street, nestled in the charming town of Newton, NC. This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers an inviting canvas for those dreaming of personalizing their living space. This property presents a wonderful opportunity to infuse your own style and design.

Outside, the property features a generous backyard, ideal for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing under the Carolina blue skies.

Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or an investor, 1977 Gail Street offers an affordable entry into a friendly community with the promise of making it your very own.
